gitCommitMessage:
Fix TypeScript build issues for Netlify

- Downgrade TypeScript from 5.8.3 to 5.4.5 for Next.js compatibility
- Standardize devDependencies version format with ^ prefixes
- Add .nvmrc file to specify Node.js 18.20.2 for consistent builds
- Update netlify.toml build command to use 'npm ci' for reliable dependency installation
- Ensure all TypeScript dependencies are properly installed in CI environment

This should resolve 'TypeScript package not found' errors in Netlify builds
